Text: How easy is it to get birth contro
Message JSON: {"userId":"b2f6e7aa-b84c-441f-9dd7-5b0f51dd123b","text":"How easy is it to get birth contro"}

Text: Birth control is super easy to get. I know it sounds like a lot of work but seriously, it’s not that bad. There was a time when you could ONLY get it through your doctor but these days, you can get lots of different kinds online. Yes girl, online! Condoms, the pill, patch, ring, and even the morning after pill are available. You just need to answer a few questions and maybe meet with a doctor online and that’s it! Check out these websites to find online birth control: Prjkt Ruby, The Pill Club, Nurx, and Vagisil.

Text: What are the requirements to get birth control
Message JSON: {"userId":"b2f6e7aa-b84c-441f-9dd7-5b0f51dd123b","text":"What are the requirements to get birth control"}

Text: Birth control is super easy to get. And you don’t even need your parent’s permission to get it! Check out Planned Parenthood or Family Planning Service. Bring ID (school ID, permit, or license works), your insurance card if you have it, or monthly income/school schedule if you don’t. That’s it. They’ll help you out and get you what you need from there.
